      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained. The exterior paint retains a strong luster, though some minor stone chips and very light surface scratches are visible upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only minimal wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and drives smoothly, with all major systems functioning as intended. It represents a dependable choice for anyone seeking a well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road.",
