      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to enjoy the open road in this wonderful find! This car is in good condition and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth and dependable ride that you can rely on for years to come. It\u2019s clean, reliable, and ready for its next adventure with a new owner who appreciates a solid, well-maintained vehicle!",
