    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. Mechanically, the engine starts and runs consistently, but you should expect some minor fluid seeps and a suspension that feels a bit soft. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It is a functional car that would benefit from some cosmetic attention and routine maintenance to keep it in good working order.",
